reviewText: This is not a fixed gear movie.
it was a good movie. it was way to short 27 minutes really come on guys you could have stetched it out a bit longer. but i did like it just not long enough for me as soon as it started it was over.
won it in an amateur bike race. procrastinated about watching it for 3 days before  watching it on repeat for about three hours haha. well worth the [...] bucks IMO.
